
Three versions of this project can be build.

1. A KDE4 tray application

To build this project as a KDE tray application,you need the following packages and their development versions installed
KDE4
Qt4
g++
gcc
cmake

To build,run the following commands in the source folder

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`kde4-config --prefix` -DQT_BUILD=false -DQT5=false -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=release  ..
make
make install

2. A Qt4 tray application

To build this project as a Qt tray application,you need the following packages and their development versions installed
Qt4
g++
gcc
cmake

To build,run the following commands in the source folder

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DQT_BUILD=true -DQT5=false -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=release  ..
make
make install

3. Qt5 application
To build this project as a Qt tray application,you need the following packages and their development versions installed
Qt5
g++
gcc
cmake

To build,run the following commands in the source folder

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DQT5=true -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=release  ..
make
make install
